          <source>To make the scroll bar appear</source>
        </trans-unit>
        <trans-unit id="105" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>Set a maximum width for the widest element by calling <bpt id="p1">[</bpt>CListBox::SetHorizontalExtent<ept id="p1">](../mfc/reference/clistbox-class.md#clistbox__sethorizontalextent)</ept> in your code.</source>
        </trans-unit>
        <trans-unit id="106" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>Without this value set, the scroll bar will not appear, even when the items in the list box are wider than the box.</source>
